1b:T436,Internal evidence consistently describes interlocking screws for the KET SS nail system. These are accessory components, not standalone implants. Entity type is 'instrument' (component/accessory) rather than implant. Current title 'SS Nail Screws' is ambiguous—could mean screws FOR nails or screws made of nail material. Corrected to 'KET Interlocking Screws' for clinical clarity. Material confirmed as Stainless Steel from both product_id (ket-ss-nail-screws) and classification. No external sources available to verify KET system details or anatomy scope, but intramedullary nailing typically applies to long bones. Division 'Trauma' and category 'Bone Screws' support fracture fixation context. Recommend merging into parent 'KET Nailing System' product family page as these are system components, not standalone products. Review required due to: (1) no brand specified, (2) no external validation available, (3) specific anatomy targets unknown, (4) component-level item that should likely be presented within parent system context rather than as separate catalog entry.16:["$","$L1a",null,{"product":{"product_name":"KET SS Nail Screws","product_name_display":"SS Nail Screws","sku_code":"KET-SS-SCREW","product_family":"KET Nailing System","product_family_display":"KET Nailing System","slug":"ket-ss-nail-screws","images":[{"id":"prop_69c49ff","storage_path":"agile-ortho/products/69c49ff221c25bab426785e9/cover_b216f7c0.jpg","original_filename":"cover_Ket-SS Nail Catalogue.pdf.jpg","content_type":"image/jpeg","size":403003,"uploaded_at":"2026-03-26T05:56:23.519759+00:00","source":"family_propagation","width":3308,"height":2339}],"status":"published","live_visible":true,"brochure_url":"","seo_meta_title":"SS Nail Screws | KET Nailing System Bone Screws - MedDevice Pro Telangana","seo_meta_description":"Meril's Ket Ss Nail Catalogue is a professional-grade trauma implant system. ","pack_size":"Individual sterile packaging","size_variables":"Various lengths and diameters","c